Embedding service usage should utilize the `embedding.py` file,
which provides a `local_embedding(inputs)` function for obtaining text embeddings.
To use the embedding service, call `local_embedding` with a list of input texts.
Example:
     from embedding import local_embedding
     vectors = local_embedding(["Your text here"])
     # `vectors` will be a list of embedding vectors corresponding to the input texts.
 